xmas.c demo from pdcurses for NativeClient

RUNNING
=======
Have a webserver running in $(NATIVECOLORS_ROOT)
http://<server>:<port>/examples/curses_xmas/

BUILDING
========
make publish
- makes nexe for distribution

make devel
- makes development nexe, you will need to change nmf file

make devel-debug
- makes development debug nexe, you will need to change nmf file

make gcc
- makes special local only test copy of xmas.c. pdcurses/ecma-48 TESTING ONLY.

make all
- makes all variations of nexes 

